Moncler CEO Quits; Chairman Ruffini to Assume CEO Powers

-- B y   M a r c o   B e r t a c c h e
-- 
2011-10-13T13:35:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/moncler-ceo-quits-chairman-ruffini-to-assume-ceo-powers.html
Moncler Group said Alberto Lavia
quit as chief executive officer, according to an e-mailed
statement.  Chairman Remo Ruffini will assume CEO powers, the statement
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marco Bertacche at 
 mbertacche@bloomberg.net  